{"tid":2359724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"校方大搞「政治綠化」 港大不容連儂牆 栽花殺自由","createTime":"2021-01-09T06:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T09:15:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa2ba9c773b7b96b79ca3070adc160087654e42a","tid":2359724,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:37:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/MURHHAVKVVFDDMK6RI4FCKPPVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FMURHHAVKVVFDDMK6RI4FCKPPVE%2F&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXVQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=2ce202d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FMURHHAVKVVFDDMK6RI4FCKPPVE%2F&h=698bbfb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/MURHHAVKVVFDDMK6RI4FCKPPVE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n校方大搞「政治綠化」<br />\n港大不容連儂牆 栽花殺自由<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vZpfVjwf7-br1QRjsnepWOtV6_s=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GDNTL2F5SZGV5PGQ7J4GKOHNJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvZpfVjwf7-br1QRjsnepWOtV6_s%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGDNTL2F5SZGV5PGQ7J4GKOHNJM.jpg&h=c4d23ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■工人昨在連儂牆裝上可掛盆栽的金屬支架，有位置已擺放綠色膠籃（箭嘴示）。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港大去年拆除連儂牆並收回管理權，校方近日更以該處人流眾多為由，決定「綠化」該牆並拆卸枱凳。原為連儂牆位置昨裝上綠色膠籃，並有工人加固可裝上盆栽的木製背板。學生會嘆校園已失去僅存言論自由空間。<br />\n<br />\n前年反送中運動期間，港大大學街上層攤位位置化身貼滿文宣的連儂牆，但校方去年10月以「安全及管理考慮」為由，在協議期屆滿後向港大學生會收回該址管理權，並以水馬圍封及清拆連儂牆。港大學生會刊物《學苑》報道指，校方本周二派員到該處在原連儂牆位置掛上植物盆栽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1qPBT9drwgnpfj4qY2sVlVa60Og=/2103x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KEE763EWAND23LYUXTYPI3EEAI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1qPBT9drwgnpfj4qY2sVlVa60Og%3D%2F2103x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKEE763EWAND23LYUXTYPI3EEAI.jpg&h=b69b9edd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■反送中運動期間，港大連儂牆成為學生表達訴求的唯一地方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dgMogrFb8A9Io7YsYlNEaKZBbDM=/3593x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BOSLMHTQDVHRNATZNUO6UC7LFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdgMogrFb8A9Io7YsYlNEaKZBbDM%3D%2F3593x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBOSLMHTQDVHRNATZNUO6UC7LFQ.jpg&h=0b84e145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港大校方去年拆除大學街的連儂牆，更以水馬圍封阻止學生接近。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學生會斥理據牽強<br />\n<br />\n本報記者昨實地視察，發現原連儂牆位置已裝上可掛上盆栽的木製背板，有工人裝上金屬支架加固。有港大學生周一晚發現該處被掛上植物盆栽，昨日見到部份位置裝上幾個綠色膠籃。<br />\n<br />\n港大學生會會長葉芷琳指，去年。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n該會外務副會長鄭凱盈補充，攤位。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港大回覆查詢時指，由於大學街位於港鐵站出口，人流眾多，故會將該地段綠化並騰出寬敞的空間通道；又指大學將繼續與學生會討論，物色其他適合學生活動的地方。<br />\n<br />\n港大連儂牆去年7月底及9月底被收回管理權前，兩度受大規模破壞。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n噤聲之風蔓延至校園，多間大學的連儂牆去年被移除，連由學生會管理的民主。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中大學生會會長蘇浚峰則指，校園內連儂大道和油漆標語早被校方「修復」，校方。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7Q2VPopBv-gA4IufZ8OZmpAChso=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N4HR3SEF4NHHTKN7AOGOHFBVTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7Q2VPopBv-gA4IufZ8OZmpAChso%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN4HR3SEF4NHHTKN7AOGOHFBVTQ.jpg&h=bcd6b6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港大學生會長葉芷琳（左）及外務副會長鄭凱盈（右）質疑校方企圖滅聲。"},{"pid":"f983e979375625ff6947fa8626ef801034315ca4","tid":2359724,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T07:41:39.000Z","msg":"港大火魔師"},{"pid":"5c256b6252d452a60baaed4fbf8993b36b017716","tid":2359724,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c478e7d237f8c00e7dd9010c47fe53ac17414c45","tid":2359724,"uid":283700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:07:39.000Z","msg":"自由花？ 放部機日日播64"},{"pid":"6973ff54e3622aade2bdcd9cb80ec3a461e06c45","tid":2359724,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"0539c30b038afd246adbd0b41cf683f53c78c4ef","tid":2359724,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"同中共 &quot;綠化&quot; 荒山一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自欺欺人"},{"pid":"dea1d18b855286ae3829a98f90e53edd0b5ce0a8","tid":2359724,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:15:22.000Z","msg":"XGDX<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}